I have a hot key set up for when I pull that tells the group I am Mezzing/Charming X MoB.  But what of the case of two Sarnak Recruits?  I normally would have the tanks assist me after a pull when using Lullaby.  But if I have to target the Mob to Charm/Mez and want the group to attack the other, what then?<br>
<br>
3.)  How do you time your re-charm/mez of Solon's/Pixie Stike?<br>
What I am looking for is the maximum effect and least amount of uncharmed/unmezzed time here.<br>
<br>
4.)  I was also accused of KS'ing last night.  So does Solon's Song of the Siren's have an aggro effect on any other MoBs than the one you are charming?<br>
Or is it more likely that the fellow had just utilized to soft a pull and when I ran by his pull with my train his MoB just aggroed to me normally?  (While practicing these new techniques I do tend to use a good chunk of the zone).<br>
<br>
